config permissions
------------------
https://www.reddit.com/r/i3wm/comments/3dub5d/how_to_start_polkit/


sudo groupadd docker
sudo usermod --append --groups libvirt `whoami`
sudo usermod --append --groups docker `whoami`
sudo systemctl start docker


